SlideShowPro is an ActionScript 
2.0 component for Flash MX 2004, 
Flash 8 and Flash CS3 that helps 
you display photo galleries and 
slideshows on your own web site. 
With over 60 customizable 
options, SlideShowPro works how 
you want it to, and can easily 
be styled and resized to match 
your existing site design.

www.SlideShowPro.net
